cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on object detection and segmentation using RGB-D images, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and decision forests (cs.AI) for these tasks. Additionally, the paper proposes a new geocentric embedding for depth images (cs.NE) that improves the performance of the object detection system.
